Subject: [PATCH v2] platform/x86: hdaps: switch to using polled mode of input
 devices
Message-ID: <20191001185937.GA49109@dtor-ws>
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=us-ascii
Content-Disposition: inline
